name: FoFiX
body:
### FoFiX (Frets On Fire X)
FoFiX is a rhythm game inspired by many of the popular commercial games, it is a fork of Frets on fire. Development has been pretty slow over the years but we are still here chugging away.

## Join us!
We have large plans for the game and not enough developers to reach goals quickly, if you want to help out head on over to irc #fofix at oftc.net. You can also join us at [![Gitter](https://badges.gitter.im/fofix/fofix.svg)](https://gitter.im/fofix/fofix?utm_source=badge&utm_medium=badge&utm_campaign=pr-badge&utm_content=body_badge)

## Download
We don't yet have a downloads section but this is coming soon.
